data.description: Welcome home to this 3 bedroom, 2 bath  in Winchester Ridge. This home includes an eat in kitchen, formal dining and family room with additional area that can be used as an office or den. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances and a tile backsplash. The primary suite has vaulted ceilings, a large walk in closet,  double sinks and a large shower. The back yard is fully fenced and has a nice sized screened in porch. This home is priced to sell!
